'''伊日·哈耶克'''（{{lang-cs|Jiří Hájek}}；{{bd|1913年|6月6日|1993年|10月22日|}}），[[捷克斯洛伐克|捷克斯洛伐克]]的政治家和外交家，曾先后担任驻英国大使、教育部长、外交部长。1977年他是[[七七宪章|七七宪章]]的发起成员之一。1989年之后曾担任[[亚历山大·杜布切克|亚历山大·杜布切克]]的顾问。1993年因癌症病逝。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.willy-brandt-biography.com/contemporaries/h-k/hajek-jiri/ |title=Personal Information: Jiří Hájek (1913-1993) |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809084343/https://www.willy-brandt-biography.com/contemporaries/h-k/hajek-jiri/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.britannica.com/biography/Jiri-Hajek |title=Jiri Hajek {{!}} Czech politician {{!}} Britannica |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808070456/https://www.britannica.com/biography/Jiri-Hajek |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://biblio.hiu.cas.cz/authorities/4620 |title=Hájek, Jiří, 1913-1993 |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2019-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506131303/https://biblio.hiu.cas.cz/authorities/4620 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://zivotopisyonline.cz/jiri-hajek-661913-22101993-jeden-z-prvnich-trech-mluvcich-charty-77/ |title=Jiří Hájek (6.6.1913 – 22.10.1993) |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2014-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726165224/http://zivotopisyonline.cz/jiri-hajek-661913-22101993-jeden-z-prvnich-trech-mluvcich-charty-77/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[https://data.bnf.fr/en/11526026/jiri_hajek/ Jiří Hájek (1913-1993) - Data BNF]</ref>

